<section class="band"><div class="shell">
  <p class="eyebrow">After checkout</p>
  <h2>What happens after you buy a kit.</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <article class="card"><h3>Stripe verifies payment</h3><p>Checkout sends the product SKU to Stripe and returns you to ApprovalPrep after payment.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Files unlock</h3><p>Every paid product is a direct paid download. You get the PDF guide and editable DOCX file for the kit you purchased.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>You stay in control</h3><p>ApprovalPrep does not store your letter answers or send anything for you. You review and send your own materials.</p></article>
